**********************************
Description
**********************************
Project creates a website with author's favourite movies. User is able to see a selection of posters, click on each poster to run trailer.

**********************************
Requirements to run the programme
**********************************
1. Python 2.7.6, author tried to run with python 3.3 without issues.
2. On your browser of choise plugins should be isntalled to run youtube trailers.
4. All 3 *.py files should be in the same folder.
5. Internet connection required.

**********************************
How to run?
**********************************
1. Place all three files in the same folder.
2. Run entertainment.py in terminal as "python entertainment.py"

